room_title: Escape room "The Asylum" by Escape Manor in Panama City
room_description: A sad, secret child birthed and raised inside the walls of the crumbling Asylum. Death and disappearances near the abandoned Asylum are shrouded in mystery. The community knows that something wrong is lurking in the darkness, luring in those foolish enough to come close. Victims are watched by someone or something closely for an hour… Can they escape? Can you? Struggle to solve clues and plan your escape before you’re lobotomized, becoming a patient forever at the Asylum!
